title: Alnylam Pharmaceuticals CEO on Development Goals, Profitability
description: Alnylam Pharmaceuticals CEO Yvonne Greenstreet discusses the company's development goals and being on the verge of profitability during an interview at the JPM Health-Care Conference in San Francisco. (Source: Bloomberg)
